--------------------------
Sketch : a_While_Loop
--------------------------

This sketch demonstrates how to repeat an instruction
using the while loop.

The process is thus :
-----------------------
  > Declare & initialise a variable
    > Declare a condition / a test
      > If test is TRUE THEN ...
        > ... proceed with the statement
          and continue as long as test is TRUE
            > If test is FALSE THEN ...
              > ... exit the structure
                and continue with other statements that may be in the program.
